  <brief_title>Influence of Two Different PEEP Niveaus and a Trendelenburg Positioning Manoeuvre on Subclavian Vein Diameter</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Two Different PEEP Niveaus and a Trendelenburg Positioning Manoeuvre on Subclavian Vein Diameter as a Surrogate Parameter in Punctures of Central Veins</official_title>
